{"metadata":{"title":"OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeColorSemanticTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Class"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"color semantic tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"multiple"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or not, and expose them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic013ColorMultipleB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic05ColorB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeColorSemantic